## Input

```css
@keyframes loader {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  #{50% - $loader-icon-duration} {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  #{$i}% {
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  50%, #{75% - $loader-icon-duration}, to {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  entry 100% {
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

